      "text": "Airflow DAGs (9개)\n\n오케스트레이션\nschedule / retry / backfill\n\n실행\n[7차시] Task Mapping\n→ 라인별 Producer 병렬 실행\n→ spark_batch\n\n검증\ndrift_rows 기반 run 검증\n+ daily_report\n\n운영\nheartbeat + channel 기반 health",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Airflow DAGs (9개)\n\n오케스트레이션\nschedule / retry / backfill\n\n실행\n[7차시] Task Mapping\n→ 라인별 Producer 병렬 실행\n→ spark_batch\n\n검증\ndrift_rows 기반 run 검증\n+ daily_report\n\n운영\nheartbeat + channel 기반 health",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 73,
      "index": "aI",
      "autoResize": true
    },
